headline: Lamb Weston Stock Sees Price Target Cut by JPMorgan Alongside Industry Strains
summary: Lamb Weston Holdings, Inc. (NYSE:LW) is one of the stocks on Jim Cramer’s and analysts’ radar. On August 20, JPMorgan assumed coverage of Lamb Weston stock with a Neutral rating and set a price target of $57, lowered from $66. The firm initiated coverage on 24 stocks across food producers, food retail, and agricultural products. […]
